- DialogHost renders all 7 dialogs (Settings, DirectoryPicker, Pulse, Relay, Mesh, AgentDialog, OnboardingFlow)
- Each dialog is controlled by Zustand store state
- Component is exported from the widgets/app-layout barrel
- No dialog renders children when its open state is false (verify controlled dialog pattern)
