Major refactor of `SessionSidebar.tsx` from 392 lines to ~150 lines by replacing custom layout with Shadcn Sidebar sub-components and removing all dialog JSX.

## File
`apps/client/src/layers/features/session-list/ui/SessionSidebar.tsx`

## Target Structure

```tsx
import {
  Sidebar, SidebarContent, SidebarFooter, SidebarGroup,
  SidebarGroupLabel, SidebarHeader, SidebarMenu,
  SidebarMenuButton, SidebarMenuItem, SidebarRail,
} from '@/layers/shared/ui';
import { AgentHeader } from './AgentHeader';
import { AgentContextChips } from './AgentContextChips';
import { SidebarFooterBar } from './SidebarFooterBar';
// ProgressCard import for onboarding

export function SessionSidebar() {
  // Keep these hooks/logic:
  // - useSessions, useDirectoryState, createMutation
  // - handleSessionClick, justCreatedId state
  // - auto-select-first-session effect
  // - Pulse notification toast logic, tab badge logic
  // - groupedSessions memo

  return (
    <Sidebar collapsible="offcanvas">
      <SidebarHeader>
        <AgentHeader
          cwd={selectedCwd}
          onOpenPicker={() => setPickerOpen(true)}
          onOpenAgentDialog={() => setAgentDialogOpen(true)}
        />
        <NewSessionButton onClick={...} disabled={...} />
      </SidebarHeader>

      <SidebarContent>
        {groupedSessions.length > 0 ? (
          groupedSessions.map((group) => (
            <SidebarGroup key={group.label}>
              {!hideHeader && (
                <SidebarGroupLabel>{group.label}</SidebarGroupLabel>
              )}
              <SidebarMenu>
                {group.sessions.map((session) => (
                  <SidebarMenuItem key={session.id}>
                    <SidebarMenuButton
                      isActive={session.id === activeSessionId}
                      onClick={() => handleSessionClick(session.id)}
                      className="h-auto py-2"
                    >
                      <div className="flex flex-col gap-0.5 min-w-0">
                        <span className="text-muted-foreground text-xs">
                          {formatRelativeTime(session.updatedAt)}
                        </span>
                        <span className="text-muted-foreground/70 truncate text-xs">
                          {session.title}
                        </span>
                      </div>
                    </SidebarMenuButton>
                  </SidebarMenuItem>
                ))}
              </SidebarMenu>
            </SidebarGroup>
          ))
        ) : (
          <div className="...">No conversations yet</div>
        )}
      </SidebarContent>

      <SidebarFooter>
        {shouldShowOnboarding && <ProgressCard ... />}
        <AgentContextChips />
        <SidebarFooterBar />
      </SidebarFooter>

      <SidebarRail />
    </Sidebar>
  );
}
```

## What to Remove from SessionSidebar

1. **All 7 dialog JSX blocks**: SettingsDialog, DirectoryPicker, ResponsiveDialog for Pulse/Relay/Mesh, AgentDialog, OnboardingFlow step modal. These are now in DialogHost.

2. **Close button wrapper**: The `flex items-center gap-1.5` wrapper that put AgentHeader + PanelLeftClose on the same row. The close button is now `SidebarTrigger` in `SidebarInset` (in App.tsx).

3. **SessionItem expand/collapse**: Replace the existing `SessionItem` component usage with simpler `SidebarMenuButton` items showing time + title only. The detail expansion (session ID, timestamps, permission mode) is removed for cleaner sidebar.

4. **Custom scroll/container layout**: The Shadcn `SidebarContent` handles scrolling.

5. **Dialog-related local state**: `agentDialogOpen` and `onboardingStep` are now in Zustand.

6. **Dialog-related hooks/imports**: Remove imports for SettingsDialog, PulsePanel, RelayPanel, MeshPanel, AgentDialog, OnboardingFlow that were rendered inline.

## What to Keep

- `useSessions`, `useDirectoryState`, `createMutation` hooks
- `handleSessionClick` function
- `justCreatedId` state and auto-scroll behavior
- Auto-select-first-session effect
- Pulse notification toast logic
- Tab badge logic
- `groupedSessions` memoization
- `shouldShowOnboarding` check for ProgressCard

## AgentHeader Changes

The AgentHeader component now has full width of `SidebarHeader`. The props may need adjustment:
- `onOpenPicker` calls `useAppStore().setPickerOpen(true)` 
- `onOpenAgentDialog` calls `useAppStore().setAgentDialogOpen(true)`

No changes to AgentHeader's internal layout are needed.

## SidebarRail

Include `<SidebarRail />` after `<SidebarFooter>` inside the `<Sidebar>` component. This adds an invisible hover-target strip at the sidebar edge for mouse-over toggle.

## Acceptance Criteria
- SessionSidebar uses Sidebar, SidebarHeader, SidebarContent, SidebarFooter sub-components
- Session items use SidebarGroup > SidebarMenu > SidebarMenuItem > SidebarMenuButton
- `collapsible="offcanvas"` is set on Sidebar
- SidebarRail is included
- No dialog JSX remains in SessionSidebar
- No close button in SessionSidebar
- AgentHeader gets full SidebarHeader width
- File is ~150 lines (down from 392)
